headline.print_headline: Canada Blocks Rogers/Bell JV From Grabbing More Airwaves
headline.main: Canada Blocks Rogers/Bell JV From Grabbing More Airwaves

lead_paragraph: Canada blocked a joint venture of two of the country's biggest wireless telephone carriers from acquiring more airwaves on Thursday, sending the latest pointed message that their dominant positions would be challenged in the fight to win over consumers.
